### 🏰 重要設定補充 (Important Additional Settings)

-   住在一座**蜂蜜王國裡的閃閃蜂窩城堡** (Lives in a **shining honeycomb castle in the Honey Kingdom**)
-   有一隻蜜蜂侍衛團，會圍繞他飛來飛去幫他扇風 (Has a bee guard troupe that flies around him to fan him)
-   每次出巡，會自帶「bling bling」音效和蜂蜜香氣，連空氣都黏黏的，太 Kira 了！(Every time he goes on an inspection tour, he comes with "bling bling" sound effects and the scent of honey, even the air becomes sticky, so Kira!)

